        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Gouda Quesadillas with Caramelised Apple. Mexican home cooking with the heat-citrus-corn triangle at the centre. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Cookies bake fast and reward a chilled dough. Pull them out when the edges set and the middles still look slightly underdone.",
            "type": "text"
          }
